      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "For sale is a dependable vehicle in fair condition, perfect for someone looking for a functional daily driver without the premium price tag. The car runs and drives well, though it shows its age with some cosmetic blemishes on the exterior and minor wear on the interior upholstery. All major systems are operational, but expect the typical signs of use that come with a well-traveled vehicle. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that still has plenty of life left for its next owner.",
