    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, budget-friendly option for a daily driver. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows noticeable signs of use, including some interior wear, minor exterior scuffs, and a few mechanical items that will likely need attention in the near future. It has been a reliable car, but it is no longer in pristine or 'good' condition, making it ideal for someone looking for a project or an affordable way to get from A to B. We recommend a personal inspection to fully understand the maintenance it might require.",
