    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands in showroom condition. This car has been fastidiously maintained by a single owner and has spent its entire life in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, chips, or dings. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and taut, completely free of creases or wear, while the high-tech cabin retains its original factory scent. Every button, sensor, and mechanical component operates with the crisp precision of a brand-new vehicle. With a comprehensive service history exclusively from authorized dealerships and a chassis that has never seen a salted road, this is a rare find for the buyer who demands perfection. It is, quite simply, as close to new as a pre-owned vehicle can be.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
